    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 4,
    "source_text": "友邦保險中國業務在2021年錄得成功的勢頭，首兩個月的新業務價值與2020年同期比較，錄得非常強勁的增\n長。2020年新業務價值9.68億美元較2019年減少17%，主要由於2019冠狀病毒病在第一季爆發初期而導致銷售額\n有限。隨著外出限制放寬，新業務動力得以迅速改善。新業務價值重拾我們慣常的季節性規律，比重更側重於上\n半年。在2020年，友邦保險中國業務為集團的新業務價值帶來最大貢獻。",
    "current_translation": "AIA China achieved strong momentum in 2021, with VONB in the first two months recording very robust growth compared to the same period in 2020. VONB of US$968 million in 2020 decreased by 17% compared to 2019, primarily due to limited sales in the early outbreak of COVID-19 in the first quarter. As travel restrictions eased, new business momentum improved rapidly. VONB resumed our customary seasonal pattern, with a greater proportion weighted towards the first half of the year. In 2020, AIA China contributed the largest share to the Group's VONB."
  },
